{"tid":1632203,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"要令黨鐵永久全線停開","createTime":"2019-10-06T17:14:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T02:52:35.000Z","uid":189386,"like":12,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"2d40bb73378244dd3cfa8f1486a30672c66806c1","tid":1632203,"uid":189386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:14:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d9b1ea88f0641e8b63a00a235c38365a229a6dd","tid":1632203,"uid":259319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:14:59.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">[18區開花] 一句講晒，聽日一點定八點？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1631933\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1631933</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區</span></span>"},{"pid":"e6aa10671741830309f85015e235e5ac83331974","tid":1632203,"uid":328673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:22:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b714dd48e75c47745f95cae45f0f8b065ac60322","tid":1632203,"uid":49994,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:32:46.000Z","msg":"要佢跪姐，停開有乜意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54be141891b49a93be09808f1e301269f095e7ba","tid":1632203,"uid":251292,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:35:43.000Z","msg":"可以話 咁樣有啲人就有怨言<br />\n然後就會無限放大<br />\n政府就係等緊呢啲"},{"pid":"39ba916b32811214d48bb1bde00e37e922921b07","tid":1632203,"uid":15259,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:35:56.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">對店舖:記住唔需要次次硬裝修</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">1.打電話、EMAIL、無限FAX</span></span></strong><br />\n想同職員談心又得，講咩都得，幫阿SIR叫下外賣又得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />總知JAM到佢線就得。有EMAIL既就SEND EMAIL查詢下，有FAX機既可以用下無限FAX大法<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">2.MEMO紙</span></span></strong><br />\n有開門就入去叫杯水慢慢坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無開門既咪留張紙起度寫低自己有咩問或者有咩訴求囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">3.善用1823</span></span></strong><br />\n食完野集體食物中毒呀，消防設備唔合符規格呢D無理由唔投訴呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n留意返打完1823之後，佢係要起限期內比返回覆你架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢招長玩長有，大家打之前要謹慎少少呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">4.蟲系魔法師</span></span></strong><br />\n知道好多巴絲打鐘意養蟲蟲，但係入店一定要小心唔好倒瀉D寶貝呀(特別起食肆)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">對人(限影大頭相/沒有攻擊性/非主攻類):</span></strong></span><br />\n記住召喚神獸唔係唔得，必須記住係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: pink;\">對家首先用武力/拎住武器先可以召喚</span></strong></span><br />\n但係對住非攻擊形對手都召喚既話觀感就唔係太好睇，仲比左機會對家有煲大<br />\n對住非攻擊形既我地可以幫佢<strong><span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">飛個靚髮</span></span></strong>或者<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">化下妝</span></span></strong>就夠，唔一定要下下爆哂缸先叫成功架<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">*要記住中年人著緊自己把頭髮仲多過條命</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n呢場抗爭要贏一定要學識剛柔並用<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/ejjnAS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/ejjnAS</a>"},{"pid":"5b5d9669b2abea52465882a7a3534479a9c3a749","tid":1632203,"uid":113386,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b714dd48e75c47745f95cae45f0f8b065ac60322","tid":1632203,"uid":49994,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:32:46.000Z","msg":"要佢跪姐，停開有乜意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:40:25.000Z","msg":"跪邊一派都係停，<br />\n你覺得黨鐵會跪中共定跪香港人？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你又估下佢跪完一邊會唔會跪埋另一邊咁搞笑？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n要佢停駛姐，冇乜特別意思嘅"},{"pid":"482093dddd6b59b658c17ff606c0a66084dc3078","tid":1632203,"uid":167883,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T18:37:17.000Z","msg":"幾好"},{"pid":"fbd00bfd69badd1914bb2dced5cd7fc6070f4eda","tid":1632203,"uid":232237,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2d40bb73378244dd3cfa8f1486a30672c66806c1","tid":1632203,"uid":189386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:14:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T18:38:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b6ac6d51ffc40fba8a0c3d13ee1d49358139b20","tid":1632203,"uid":210001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T18:41:57.000Z","msg":"痴撚線呢啲post想點"},{"pid":"1e1c3cd144da0c877ce6cd02b90d41a77af3a1dd","tid":1632203,"uid":186851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2d40bb73378244dd3cfa8f1486a30672c66806c1","tid":1632203,"uid":189386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:14:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"201